Title: title: 'This week in Nushell #335'
Path: Nushell
Content:
@cablehead:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17398] added content-type metadata for ndjson, nuon, ndnuon in std/formats (#17398)
@fdncred:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17396] added short params to join (#17396)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17395] bumped Rust toolchain to 1.91.1 (#17395)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17384] added 
``explore regex``
 help popup (#17384)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17383] removed unlet vars from completions (#17383)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17382] updated 
``explore regex``
 to use 
``AltGr``
 keys (#17382)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17368] updated UseAnsiColoring with TERM=dumb (#17368)
@smartcoder0777:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17393] added --prefix/--suffix to join to disambiguate columns (#17393)
@ayax79:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17392] bumped rmcp lib from 0.8 to 0.13 (#17392)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17377] added 
``polars entropy``
 (#17377)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17365] fixed help to display aliased command when calling 
``help <alias>``
 (#17365)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17359] allowed aliasing to work on sub commands (#17359)
@kaathewisegit:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17381] made 
``it``
 a reserved variable name (#17381)
@ysthakur:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17370] bumped to dev version 0.110.1 (#17370)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17367] bumped to 0.110.0 for release (#17367)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17366] pinned reedline to 0.45 for 0.110 release (#17366)
@ChrisDenton:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17369] stopped canonicalizing config path (#17369)
@hovancik:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17178] updated closures-related tutors (#17178)
@app/dependabot:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17391] bumped lsp-textdocument from 0.4.2 to 0.5.0 (#17391)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17390] bumped shadow-rs from 1.5.0 to 1.6.0 (#17390)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17388] bumped crate-ci/typos from 1.42.0 to 1.42.1 (#17388)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17347] bumped quick-xml from 0.38.3 to 0.39.0 (#17347)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17344] bumped data-encoding from 2.9.0 to 2.10.0 (#17344)
